- npm install -g expo-cli
- npx create-expo-app mobile --template
- install expo in your phone
- run the application: npx expo start
- scan the QR Code in the Expo app at device
- create src folder, with its ouw assets folder
- Import the font inter from google fonts: npx expo install expo-font @expo-google-fonts/inter 
- install tailwind para Native: 
    npm i nativewind
    npm i tailwindcss --save-dev
- npx tailwind init
- completar arquivo babel.config com:
    plugins: ['nativewind/babel']
- Library to use SVG format: 
    npx expo install react-native-svg
- Library to use SVG as a component:
    npm i react-native-svg-transformer --save-dev
- npm install dayjs
- Install navegation library:
    npm install @react-navigation/native